title: '"There''s a centralization of what we take from the past because the present is so crowded." -- Tyler Cowen, when interviewed by Patrick Collison'
pid: 44dc3814-f1e7-4e90-acab-b1929aabdbd5
body: |2-
  That is, the music, literature, etc. that people know about from past periods is dominated by biggest-hit players like The Beatles or Tolstoy.
